CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 12, 1954, pg. 4, reads: "Pitt Graduation - These young men and women were among the 1561 who were granted degrees Wednesday at the spring commencement of the University of Pittsburgh. They are, left to right:...Barbara L. Weems and Ruth L. Suiter, both graduates of the School of Nursing....-Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of University of Pittsburgh School of Nursing graduates Barbara L .Weems and Ruth L. Suiter, posed in interior
